## FAQ
**Q: Can I sync TaskManager across devices?**  
A: Yes, TaskManager supports cloud sync. Log in with the same account on multiple devices.  

**Q: Is TaskManager free?**  
A: TaskManager offers a free version with basic features. Premium plans unlock advanced features.  

